OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FFifa has announced it will release
OL,7,Fanother batch of tickets for the World
OL,8,FCup, after facing criticism over the
OL,9,Fextremely high prices during the
OL,10,Fprevious round of sales.
OL,12,FThe tournament, which is split across
OL,13,Fthe United States, Canada and Mexico,
OL,14,Fis due to kick off in less than 50
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
