OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FFifa has been heavily ridiculed by
OL,7,Fgovernments and fan clubs for the
OL,8,Fprice of the tickets, but they have
OL,9,Fbeen unfazed by the criticism and
OL,10,Frecently introduced an even higher
OL,11,Fpremium tier for each category of
OL,12,Fseats.
OL,14,FThe aggressive pricing structure may
OL,15,Fnot be paying off for Fifa, with The
OL,16,FAthletic reporting on Tuesday that
OL,17,Fticket sales are lagging for the US
OL,18,Fopener against Paraguay on June 12.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
