CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FThe US publication said a document
OL,7,Fdistributed to local organisers dated
OL,8,FApril 10 revealed that only 40,934
OL,9,Ftickets had been purchased for the US-
OL,10,FParaguay game on June 13 and only
OL,11,F50,661 for the Iran-New Zealand
OL,12,Fcontest on June 16.
OL,14,FTickets for the US game are around six
OL,15,Ftimes more expensive than tickets for
OL,16,Fthe Iran game.
OL,18,FFifa says California's SoFi stadium,
OL,19,Fwhere the opener will be played, will
OL,20,Fhave a capacity of almost 70,000
OL,21,Fduring the World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
