CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FWhen will the tickets become available
OL,7,Fand what games will they be for?
OL,9,FThey will go on sale at 11pm Eastern
OL,10,Ftime, or 4pm UK time.
OL,12,FFifa has said they will be available
OL,13,Ffor all 104 matches across the
OL,14,Ftournament.
OL,16,FThe tickets will be available at
OL,17,FFifa's website at Fifa.com/tickets,
OL,18,Fwith Fifa warning potential customers
OL,19,Fmay face a queue to access the sales
OL,20,Fplatform if demand is high.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
