PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FFifa has said the tickets will be
OL,7,Ffirst come first serve and will they
OL,8,Fwill keep releasing tickets until the
OL,9,Fend of the tournament.
OL,11,FWhat type of tickets will they be?
OL,13,FThe tickets will be for categories 1,
OL,14,F2 and 3, with category 1 being the
OL,15,Fbest tickets in the stadium.
OL,17,FThere will be no tickets in category
OL,18,F4, which are the worst seats in the
OL,19,Fstadium and also the cheapest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
