OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FCategory 1 tickets range from #330 for
OL,7,Fthe least popular teams during the
OL,8,Fgroup stage, while a top seat at the
OL,9,Ffinal with a category 1 front row
OL,10,Fticket could set you back as much as
OL,11,F#8,120.
OL,13,FFifa has also said there will be front
OL,14,Ftickets available for each category.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
