OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FThis means that each category also has
OL,7,Fa premium option, which will give the
OL,8,Fpurchaser a front-row seat within each
OL,9,Fcategory.
OL,11,FSo buying a 'front' category 2 ticket
OL,12,Fwill give the customer the best seats
OL,13,Fwithin category 2, but will still not
OL,14,Fbe as good as a seat in category 1.
OL,16,FA 'front' category 1 ticket will be a
OL,17,Ffront row seat to the match and will
OL,18,Falso be the most expensive.
OL,20,FWhat criticism has Fifa faced over
OL,21,Fticket prices in the UK?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
