OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FThe Football Supporters' Association
OL,7,Fsaid at the start of April: "This is
OL,8,Fthe most expensive World Cup in
OL,9,Fhistory for travelling supporters,
OL,10,Ffrom match tickets to travel and
OL,11,Faccommodation. It isn't just an issue
OL,12,Ffor English fans but for those across
OL,13,Fthe planet.
OL,15,F"Fifa's ridiculous ticket pricing and
OL,16,Fopaque policies have led many fans to
OL,17,Fconclude they simply can't afford to
OL,18,Fattend football's greatest global
OL,19,Fevent."
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
