CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776898985
OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FJohn Swinney, Scotland's first
OL,7,Fminister, has also written to Fifa
OL,8,Fcriticising the price of tickets.
OL,10,FIn the letter, he said the World Cup
OL,11,Fmust be a "celebration of football"
OL,12,Fand not an exercise in "making as much
OL,13,Fmoney as possible".
OL,15,FThe Football Supporters Europe group
OL,16,Fhas also lodged a complaint with Fifa
OL,17,Fover the price of tickets.
OL,26,@sD@KOUsD@cO]tD@XOUuD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
