OL,3,CHow can you get the latest batch of
OL,4,CWorld Cup tickets?
OL,6,FFifa isn't the only body that has been
OL,7,Faccused of cashing in on fans for the
OL,8,Ftournament, with it recently being
OL,9,Freported that train transport from
OL,10,FBoston South Station to Foxboro
OL,11,FStation (where both England and
OL,12,FScotland are scheduled to play) had
OL,13,Fquadrupled on game days from around
OL,14,F#15 to #60.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
